OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FA teacher accused of the sexual abuse
OL,7,Fand murder of a baby he adopted said:
OL,8,F"I'm going to hell," as he cradled the
OL,9,Fdead child, a court has heard.
OL,11,FJamie Varley, 37, who earlier wailed
OL,12,Ffor his mother, made the remark in the
OL,13,Fbereavement room at Blackpool Victoria
OL,14,FHospital with 13-month-old Preston
OL,15,FDavey in his arms.
OL,17,FFootage of the incident, along with a
OL,18,Fseries of other videos captured by
OL,19,Fpolice body worn cameras, were played
OL,20,Fto jurors at his murder trial at
OL,21,FPreston Crown Court.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FVarley is seen in apparent disbelief
OL,7,Fand guilt-ridden, blaming himself for
OL,8,Fleaving the child in the bath before
OL,9,Fclaiming he found the child face down
OL,10,Fminutes later. But prosecutors say his
OL,11,Faccount is inconsistent with post-
OL,12,Fmortem findings, which discovered the
OL,13,Fchild had 40 injuries.
OL,15,FVarley, at the time a high school
OL,16,Fteacher, is accused of the murder of
OL,17,Fthe child, while his partner, John
OL,18,FMcGowan-Fazakerley, 32, is accused of
OL,19,Fallowing the death of the child, with
OL,20,Fboth accused of sexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FDuring the four months the baby was
OL,7,Funder their adoption at their home in
OL,8,FBlackpool, he was allegedly routinely
OL,9,Fill-treated, had indecent images and
OL,10,Fvideos taken of him, was sexually
OL,11,Fabused and physically assaulted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FThe defendants had rushed the
OL,7,Funconscious child from their home,
OL,8,Fafter an alleged final sexual assault
OL,9,Fby Varley, to Blackpool hospital
OL,10,Faround 6.20pm on July 27 2023. Medics
OL,11,Fworked for nearly an hour to
OL,12,Fresuscitate the child until a decision
OL,13,Fwas made that further intervention was
OL,14,Ffutile and life was pronounced extinct
OL,15,Fat 7.20pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FJurors were shown the footage as a
OL,7,F"hysterical" Varley, accompanied by
OL,8,Fhis mother Karen Graham, collapses
OL,9,Fonto a floor inside the hospital, as
OL,10,Fmedics ask him to come to the child's
OL,11,Fbedside as they could not revive him
OL,12,Fand resuscitation attempts were to end.
OL,14,FVarley can be seen wailing: "I'm done.
OL,15,FIt's my fault. No mum, I can't get up.
OL,16,FIt's my fault. Do not give up on him.
OL,17,FThis is not happening.
OL,19,F"It's my fault, I left him for
OL,20,Fliterally two minutes. It's my fault.
OL,21,FI left him. Mum!
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]vD@]OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,F"I can't, I can't, this is not
OL,7,Fhappening. Please kill me."
OL,9,FMore footage was shown of Varley,
OL,10,Fbarefoot and wearing a Jurassic Park t-
OL,11,Fshirt and tartan pyjama bottoms,
OL,12,Foutside the hospital entrance, minutes
OL,13,Fafter Preston has been declared dead.
OL,15,FPacing back and forth, Varley said:
OL,16,F"It's not happening. He's not gone.
OL,18,F"I'm going to go in there, he's going
OL,19,Fto be smiling, he's going to be
OL,20,Flaughing. This is not happening. If
OL,21,Fhe's dead, I can't live with this."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@[O]xD@AOUzD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FVarley is also asked if he wants to go
OL,7,Fand see Preston, who he had renamed
OL,8,FElijah.
OL,10,FHe replies: "No. I don't deserve to
OL,11,Fsee him. I left him. I can't, not now
OL,12,Fplease."
OL,14,FHe continues: "I only left the
OL,15,Fbathroom to get clothes... This can't
OL,16,Fhappen.
OL,18,F"He's got his life ahead of him. I'm
OL,19,Fnot going in, because it's fine.
OL,26,@rD@MOUtD@HO]vD@OOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,F"I'm a teacher, I'm head of year, I'm
OL,7,Fchild protection trained.
OL,9,F"You don't leave him in a bath tub. He
OL,10,Fwas in his chair, he was fine.
OL,12,F"He doesn't deserve me. I should not
OL,13,Fhave left him...
OL,15,F"He was giving me cuddles when I put
OL,16,Fshampoo in his hair."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FMore video was then shown of events
OL,7,Finside the bereavement room with
OL,8,FMcGowan-Fazakerley and Varley's mother
OL,9,Fand he is cajoled to enter the room.
OL,10,FHe continues to pace up and down, and
OL,11,Fsays: "I don't want to be in here. He
OL,12,Fneeds to be warm, keep him warm.
OL,14,F"Elijah wake up. He is going to wake
OL,15,Fup mum. He's my baby boy. He's got to
OL,16,Fwake up.
OL,18,F"I need to get out of here."
OL,26,@sD@GOUvD@AOUzD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FThe next clip shows Varley outside,
OL,7,Fwhere he says: "I tried to go in but
OL,8,Fmy mum wouldn't let me hold him."
OL,10,FThe final footage shows Varley and his
OL,11,Fco-accused together at just after
OL,12,F11pm, in the bereavement room. Varley
OL,13,Fis cradling the child and McGowan-
OL,14,FFazakerley says: "It's going to be the
OL,15,Fhardest thing... we've got each other."
OL,17,FVarley is also told not to blame
OL,18,Fhimself and the death is a "tragic
OL,19,Faccident".
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@aO]vD@ROUwD@gO]zD@\OU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FVarley, still cradling the child with
OL,7,Fhis head down, responds: "I probably
OL,8,Fwon't see you again. I'm definitely
OL,9,Fgoing to hell."
OL,11,FHis co-accused continues to try to
OL,12,Fconsole him and Varley says: "They'll
OL,13,Fbe whisking me away for neglect."
OL,15,FPreston was born on June 16 2022,
OL,16,Fimmediately taken into care by Oldham
OL,17,FCouncil, and placed with foster
OL,18,Fparents at five days old.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUqD@OO]tD@^OUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FAfter undergoing an assessment and
OL,7,Ffamiliarisation process in early 2023
OL,8,Fhe was adopted and began living with
OL,9,Fthe defendants on April 1 at their
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FVarley took a year off work as head of
OL,13,Fyear and as a design and technology
OL,14,Fteacher at a local high school, South
OL,15,FShore Academy, to look after the
OL,16,Fchild, but struggled as a new parent
OL,17,Fwith a baby who frequently woke during
OL,18,Fthe night, the court has heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778223659
OL,3,C'I'm going to hell' ` teacher accused
OL,4,Cof baby murder
OL,6,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,7,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,8,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,9,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,10,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,11,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,12,Fone of distributing an indecent photo
OL,13,Fof a child, to his co-accused, and one
OL,14,Fof making an indecent photo.
OL,16,FMcGowan-Fazakerley denies allowing the
OL,17,Fdeath of a child, three counts of
OL,18,Fchild cruelty and one count of the
OL,19,Fsexual assault of a child.The trial
OL,20,Fwas adjourned until Thursday morning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
